data.description: Welcome to Cypress Creek. This one-story 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage home is great for a first-time homebuyer  It has a great open floor plan. It includes tile floors throughout the common areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Fence in the backyard for your privacy. Cypress Creek community amenities include a clubhouse, two pools with cabana areas, basketball courts, a playground, a dog park, and outdoor fitness stations. Close to shopping, restaurants, hospitals, schools and also has easy access to I-75, Hwy 301, or US41 for commuters to Sarasota, St. Pete, or Tampa!
